<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Reset Your Password | mern-setup-system</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #e0e0e0;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #0a0a0c;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #121214;
        border: 1px solid #2d2d30;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      }
      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
        padding: 40px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        margin-bottom: 5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px;
      }
      .alert-box {
        background-color: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
        border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        color: #fbbf24;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 16px 35px;
        background: #4f46e5;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 20px 0;
        transition: background 0.3s ease;
      }
      .expiry-note {
        color: #71717a;
        font-size: 13px;
        margin-top: 15px;
        word-break: break-all;
      }
      .security-tips {
        background-color: #1c1c1f;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 25px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        border: 1px solid #2d2d30;
      }
      .security-tips h3 {
        margin-top: 0;
        color: #4f46e5;
        font-size: 18px;
      }
      .security-tips ul {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
        color: #a1a1aa;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .security-tips li {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .footer {
        background-color: #0a0a0c;
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        border-top: 1px solid #2d2d30;
      }
      .support-link {
        color: #06b6d4;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .dev-credit {
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: #4f46e5;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">CODE BIRUNI</div>
        <div style="font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">Password Reset Request</div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <h2 style="color: #ffffff; margin-top: 0;">Hi {{userName}},</h2>
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account associated with the <strong>mern-setup-system</strong>.</p>

        <div class="alert-box">
          <strong>Important:</strong>
          This reset link is time-sensitive and will expire in {{expiryTime}}.
        </div>

        <p>To choose a new password, please click the button below:</p>

        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
        </p>

        <p class="expiry-note">If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:<br />
          <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="color: #06b6d4;">{{resetUrl}}</a></p>

        <div class="security-tips">
          <h3>🔒 Security Best Practices:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Never share your password or reset link with anyone.</li>
            <li>Use a unique password that you don't use on other sites.</li>
            <li>Enable Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) for maximum security.</li>
            <li>Always log out if you are using a shared computer.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #888;">If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>

        <p>Regards,<br /><strong>Code Biruni Team</strong></p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>© <span id="currentYear"></span> <strong>Code Biruni</strong>. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated security notification from <strong>mern-setup-system</strong>.</p>
        <div class="dev-credit">Engineered by Robius Sani</div>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px;">Questions? Contact 
          <a href="mailto:hafazrobiussani@gmail.com" class="support-link">hafazrobiussani@gmail.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      document.getElementById('currentYear').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>